# Skill: project-board

## Board Identity

All commands target the **Reverberage Roadmap** project board.

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Project number | `2` |
| Owner | `reverberage` |
| Project ID (GraphQL) | `PVT_kwDOEeFGTc4Bc5Ct` |

